<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Payment Receipt</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0f172a;
      padding: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 32px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #16a34a;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    p {
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 24px;
    }
    .receipt-box {
      background-color: #f0fdf4;
      border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .receipt-title {
      color: #166534;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .receipt-details {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .receipt-details td {
      padding: 6px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .label {
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .value {
      text-align: right;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 24px 32px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    }
    .footer-text {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">SaaS Subscriptions</div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Payment Receipt</h1>
        <p>Hello {{customerName}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for your renewal payment. Your subscription remains active and has been advanced to the next billing period.</p>
        
        <div class="receipt-box">
          <div class="receipt-title">Transaction Details</div>
          <table class="receipt-details">
            <tr>
              <td class="label">Invoice Number</td>
              <td class="value">{{invoiceNumber}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="label">Amount Paid</td>
              <td class="value">{{currency}} {{amountPaid}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="label">Status</td>
              <td class="value" style="color: #16a34a;">PAID</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="label">Next Billing Date</td>
              <td class="value">{{periodEnd}}</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p>If you need a copy of this invoice, you can access it via your account dashboard.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p class="footer-text">
          &copy; 2026 SaaS Inc. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
